{% block subject %}
    {% spaceless %}
        Specialty School Application Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission }}
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}
Hi {{ submission.parentEmail }},

Guardian of {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }}

RE: Specialty School Application Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission }}

Your application to the Specialty School Program for {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }} for {{ submission.openEnrollment }} has not been awarded a placement; however, your student has been added to the wait list for the following program(s):

{{ awardedSchools|raw|striptags }}

This wait list will be kept active for six weeks beyond the first day of school for {{ submission.openEnrollment }}. Should a slot become available for your student while the wait list is active you will receive a call from the Office of Specialty School Programs.

Please save this email and/or record this confirmation number for your records.

Please add specialty@tusc.k12.al.us to your address list to ensure you receive future status updates of your application.

This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies.  {{ 'magnet.contact'|trans|raw }}

Thanks,
Specialty School Program
{% endblock body_text %}

